 />終於有故"},{"pid":"d6dc00c87eaa9b9551d216e5bd0d8d0683b9f30c","tid":1651810,"uid":333301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"521b116daa0cdaa6b5b20afd3a0db6825378a3df","tid":1651810,"uid":45173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b9ed028ff92afc9747b84a01fd259d9bf1243efc","tid":1651810,"uid":333301,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:55:08.000Z","msg":"係咪淨係得我一個睇錯變成吳克儉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:56:47.000Z","msg":"你這個black object是不是豬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:16:37.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd2de67b271a80b0a377ee3464dc30fe9532196","tid":1651810,"uid":1408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:16:45.000Z","msg":"我出糧比你，你打我呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3efda222c38ecf25a86e5a3fde652572304465","tid":1651810,"uid":45173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:34:19.000Z","msg":"肥芝有想過退款，以後唔撚幫襯，但她簽了合約，要一輩子都供養他們店的牛郎，不能毀約。<br />\n<br />\n生於這個時代，有誰不是身不由己呢？<br />\n<br />\n本來以為牛郎可以帶來歡樂和平，保護自己弱小的心靈，柔弱的身軀，怎料到會這樣呢！？<br />\n<br />\n肥芝擦了擦身體，把歡愛後的汗水擦掉，連同自己的眼淚。<br />\n<br />\n克經看到了，恥笑了一聲，「哭什麼哭，你以為我真的是愛與正義的化身嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n肥芝不敢出聲，她在忍。<br />\n<br />\n忍下去，"},{"pid":"98623b678cfd25f925644ac6f1d04b4746fb4089","tid":1651810,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"有肥芝就要推"},{"pid":"599aabbb73a7827cafab2985536272c37e912de4","tid":1651810,"uid":191391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:30:39.000Z","msg":"小嘴 我好掛豬你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0c6bc1b076b5018464d9c899d952ed917aab3d","tid":1651810,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:31:05.000Z","msg":"借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑撚死，五毛入侵連登開始帶風向同國難五金割蓆。成班懵撚爭住和應<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1652399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1652399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1464675dbbada591c7a3ac3a8d810b8950318782","tid":1651810,"uid":45173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"599aabbb73a7827cafab2985536272c37e912de4","tid":1651810,"uid":191391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:30:39.000Z","msg":"小嘴 我好掛豬你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T00:49:37.000Z","msg":"唔出文應下景就對唔住自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1998a583ca9509edc98f9ed4e17f64693413658c","tid":1651810,"uid":129274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fatcmoji/fat021.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亀巴！！"},{"pid":"89bdcdde07ba9b048aa483ef5d52b56e9bab25fc","tid":1651810,"uid":39064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fatcmoji/fat025.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fatcmoji/fat025.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0464b8055b33cca2989b7ef1a3b28c47c87cffa","tid":1651810,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fatcmoji/fat015.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fatcmoji/fat015.gif\" clas